symposium under the title of "The Future of the Arab World
and the Role of the Arab League." The three-day seminar will
be opened on Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
organizers said that during the symposium, Arab officials and
political experts will discuss issues such as Arab-Arab
relations, Arab-Israeli relations and Arab relations with
Superpowers. 
