summit to a six-point comprehensive plan to facilitate the
development of Russia.
</P>
<P>
Nihon Keizai:
</P>
<P>
-- Hashimoto will propose resolving a territorial row between
Japan and Russia over a Russian-held chain of islands off northern
Japan within this century.
</P>
<P>
Asahi:
</P>
<P>
--Japan's International Trade and Industry Ministry and
Education and Culture Ministry will prepare a legislation to
promote university-to-industry technology transfers. 
</P>
</TEXT>
