<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Final Medal Table for Disabled Table Tennis Tourney </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, November 1 (Xinhua) -- Final medal table for the
inaugural Far East and South Pacific Table Tennis Championships
for the Disabled which closed here on Saturday (tabulated under
are team, gold, silver, bronze and total medals):
</P>
<P>
1. Chinese Taipei 4  7  5 16
</P>
<P>
2. Japan  4  5  4 13
</P>
<P>
3. South Korea  4  1  8 13
</P>
<P>
4. Hong Kong, China 3  3  6 12
</P>
<P>
5. China  3  2  4  9
</P>
<P>
6. Thailand  0  0  1  1
</P>
